description: Try our easy to follow Grilled Chicken & Peach Salad recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Grilled Chicken & Peach Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk oil, balsamic vinegar, honey and ginger together in a bowl. Slice chicken breasts. Arrange rocket, onion, peach, pecans and chicken on plates. Drizzle dressing over. Serve.
